---
import { FloatingIslandNavbar } from '../components/Floating.jsx';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>About - Case Study Projects</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <FloatingIslandNavbar client:load />

    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-6 space-y-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">About Our Project & Community</h1>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Objective</h2>
        <p>
          Use real-world cases to build projects that align with your mission and portfolio,
          involving the community in decision-making.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Selection Process</h2>
        <p>
          Careful research and selection of cases based on relevancy and industry growth ensures
          impactful projects built collaboratively.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Template</h2>
        <p>
          Use a simple format to define problem statements, datasets, and roadmaps that guide
          development and community contributions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Voting Mechanism</h2>
        <p>
          Share case studies publicly and integrate a voting system on the website. Community votes
          help prioritize projects, with data visualized on a public dashboard.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">Outcome</h2>
        <p>
          Selected cases progress into live projects influenced by continuous voting, feedback,
          and collaboration with the community.
        </p>
      </section>


    </main>
  </body>
</html>
